<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Melofest - FAQ</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/faq.css">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/breadcrumb.css">
</head>

<body>
  <%- include('../partials/navbar') %>
    <br><br>
    <div style="width: 75%" class="container">
      <ul class="breadcrumb">
        <li><a href="/">Home</a></li>
        <li>FAQ</li>
      </ul>

      <div class="title">
        <hr>
        <h1> FAQ </h1>
        <hr>
      </div>

      <div class="tabs">
        <h2>General</h2>
        <hr>
        <div class="tab">
          <input type="checkbox" id="rd1" name="rd">
          <label class="tab-label" for="rd1">How are payments made at the festival?</label>
          <div class="tab-content">
            Since 2022, all payments are made via an online system. It is linked to the chip on your bracelet. Thanks to
            Payconiq, you'll be able to recharge it on the app or at the charging stations to use it to pay on the
            festival.
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="tab">
          <input type="checkbox" id="rd2" name="rd">
          <label class="tab-label" for="rd2">What is the festival schedule?</label>
          <div class="tab-content">The festival opens at 12:30 and closes at 2:00 am</div>
        </div>

        <div class="tab">
          <input type="checkbox" id="rd3" name="rd">
          <label class="tab-label" for="rd3">What can I bring to the festival ?</label>
          <div class="tab-content">TIP: Don't come to the festival with unnecessary items. If possible, do not bring a
            backpack or purse.
            The following are not allowed on site: <br>
            <ul>
              <li>Weapons, explosive, flammable or volatile substances.</li>
              <li>Illegal substances, drugs.</li>
              <li>Strollers</li>
              <li>Dangerous, sharp or blunt objects, umbrellas, as well as any object likely to be used as a projectile.
              </li>
              <li>Animals (with the exception of guide dogs for visually impaired persons).</li>
              <li>Non-drinkable liquids and gels in containers larger than 100 ml.</li>
              <li>Tripods and selfie poles, lasers, drones</li>
              <li>Large backpacks (> 45 cm height)</li>
              <li>Gas and gas burners</li>
              <li>Any other object that may be considered dangerous by the organization</li>
            </ul>
            Any other object that may be considered dangerous by the organization
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="tab">
          <input type="checkbox" id="rd4" name="rd">
          <label class="tab-label" for="rd4">What is the minimum age to attend the festival?</label>
          <div class="tab-content">The minimum age to attend the festival is 16 years old. You will be asked to show
            your ID at the entrance.</div>
        </div>


        <br>
        <h2>Tickets</h2>
        <hr>
        <div class="tab">
          <input type="checkbox" id="rd5" name="rd">
          <label class="tab-label" for="rd5">How can I buy tickets?</label>
          <div class="tab-content">You can buy tickets on tickermaster. You can also buy tickets at the entrance of the
            festival, but it will be more expensive.</div>
        </div>

        <div class="tab">
          <input type="checkbox" id="rd6" name="rd">
          <label class="tab-label" for="rd6">I want to exchange my ticket</label>
          <div class="tab-content">To exchange your ticket, go to your order via the link "Manage my order" that you
            received in the confirmation email sent to you, to get to your order. <br>
            If you can't find the email, you can have it sent again here. <br>
            Then click on "Additional actions" and then on "Change tickets". <br>
            Then the system will ask you which ticket(s) you want to exchange. When you confirm the ticket you want to
            exchange, on the next page you will see the passes and day tickets you want to exchange.
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="tab">
          <input type="checkbox" id="rd7" name="rd">
          <label class="tab-label" for="rd7">How do I activate refund protection ?</label>
          <div class="tab-content">If you'd like a refund and you've taken out BOOKING PROTECT insurance with your
            ticket, it's easy - just go <a href="#">here</a></div>
        </div>

        <br>
        <h2>Mobility</h2>
        <hr>
        <div class="tab">
          <input type="checkbox" id="rd8" name="rd">
          <label class="tab-label" for="rd8">How do I get to the festival?</label>
          <div class="tab-content">The festival is located in the city center of Manchester. You can get there by train,
            bus, tram or metro. <br>
            The address is: <br>
            123 Main Street, Machnester, MA, 01944</div>
        </div>
      </div>


    </div>
    <br><br>

    <%- include('../partials/footer') %>
</body>

</html>